# Representatives

	<StatusPill status="partial" />

	Representatives sit between profile, civic identity, and comparison. The route family matters
	because PARA does not want policy participation to stop at generic posting or user follow graphs.
</section>

<section class="docs-section-card">
	<p class="docs-section-kicker">Routes</p>
## Primary routes
	<div class="docs-meta-grid">
